{"type": "article", "id": 25242, "title": "楼梯柜", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-11T06:59:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703123758BFeNxwqU8z5WnbfH.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这个立柜兼有楼梯的功能，它由 9 个抽屉盒构成，最下面三个可以拉出来构成台阶。设计师想要节约空间而设计了这个有 2.6 米高的柜子，但同时高度也带来了新的不方便，因而产生了楼梯的设计。他还有一个柜子将抽屉换成了开放的格子，设计原理相同，也都给生活带来了灵活和变化。设计师 Danny Kuo 是出生在荷兰的华人，目前在上海工作，<a href=\"http://www.dannykuo.com/index.html\">这里是他的主页</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123754G0UjqNb8ERlgMZsv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75451264\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123755GFCmUHQ7hvVebOdR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123756k2NK35iVhqQWtozM.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50234742\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703123756s3xiELCaqYTpSneB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50234742\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}